[{"date":"1955-04-30","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/da/7f/634779_0bcBJ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/da/7f/634779_0bcBJ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/da/7f/634779_0bcBJ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/da/7f/634779_0bcBJ.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/da/7f/634779_0bcBJ.jpg"},"summary":"       阳光明媚的一天，慈祥的狗父史派克答应要带乖巧的儿子泰克去郊外野餐，他怀着喜悦的心情向提篮内放入各种美食，然而两名不速之客搅了史派克的兴致。他们是在院子内上演追逐大战的汤姆和杰瑞，杰瑞敏捷地钻入提篮，汤姆则不顾一切胡乱翻弄。汤姆粗暴的举动热闹了史派克，他愤怒地将这只不识时务的老猫扔了出去。\r\n　　镜头转到郊外，史派克父子悠闲地漫步河边，杰瑞则躺在提篮内分外满足。当看到汤姆尾随而至时，杰瑞将一根香肠伪装成老鼠的模样，结果傻瓜汤姆中计，拖着香肠和史派克跑出了很远。看来，史派克父子的野餐计划注定要被一群不速之客破坏了……","name":"Pup on a Picnic","name_cn":"父子野餐","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1950s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"猫和老鼠","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"父子野餐"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1955年4月30日"},{"key":"片长","value":"7分钟"},{"key":"IMDb","value":"tt0048520"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":4,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":2,"7":0,"8":1,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.3},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":0,"wish":0,"collect":6,"doing":0},"id":634779,"eps":0,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1955-04-25","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/ae/b4/136841_6W23p.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/ae/b4/136841_6W23p.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/ae/b4/136841_6W23p.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/ae/b4/136841_6W23p.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/ae/b4/136841_6W23p.jpg"},"summary":"　　Blinkity Blank is a fine example of music creating image, the sounds you hear are mimiked it seems with the forms and flow of motion that is on the screen. From fireworks to Egyptian forms and birdcages, over a blue surface, the images being etched